\"ngram\": \"inParis\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britishsculptor Dr Willard Wigan, who has created the world's smallest handmade micro-art, meticulously crafted a miniature version of the Olympic mascot, Phryge, in a feat which involved holding his breath, working between heartbeats and using his pulse as a jackhammer.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willard_Wigan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Willard Wigan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willard_Wigan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willard_Wigan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's smallest handmade micro\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 476}, {\"ngram\": \"a miniature version\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic mascot\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 540}, {\"ngram\": \"Phryge\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"a feat\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 559}, {\"ngram\": \"his breath\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"heartbeats\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"his pulse\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"a jackhammer\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The handmade microscopic version of the official mascot, the smallest in Olympic history, can be seen holding a medal which was crafted from 24-carat gold and is roughly the size of a blood cell.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The handmade microscopic version\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"the official mascot\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic history\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"24-carat gold\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"roughly the size\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"a blood cell\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr Wigan also used an eyelash as a paintbrush to capture theFrenchflag and the Olympic rings which adorn the mascot's chest were also made from 24-carat gold.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 860, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wigan_Athletic_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.8091426151217302, \"rank\": 0.1501961089989556, \"text\": \"Wigan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wigan_Athletic_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wigan_Athletic_F.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an eyelash\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"a paintbrush\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"theFrenchflag\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic rings\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"the mascot's chest\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"24-carat gold\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The micro-sculptor, who holds a Guinness World Record for the world's smallest handmade sculpture, said: \\\"I saw the mascot Phryge and found it so cute, I wanted to create something that would capture its essence on the smallest scale possible.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1049, \"end\": 1070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guinness_World_Records\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Guinness World Record\", \"types\": [\"Q571\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guinness_World_Records\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guinness_World_Records\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The micro\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"sculptor\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1035}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's smallest handmade sculpture\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"the mascot Phryge\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"its essence\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"the smallest scale\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never enjoy the process, but the joy comes from the reaction that people have when they see it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1361, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"the joy\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"the reaction\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The artwork, which uses a microscopic magnet to secure the mascot's feet, took five weeks to complete, with Dr Wigan working for around 16 hours a day on the project.\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1474, \"end\": 1479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wigan_Athletic_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.8091426151217302, \"rank\": 0.1501961089989556, \"text\": \"Wigan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wigan_Athletic_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wigan_Athletic_F.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The artwork\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"a microscopic magnet\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"the mascot's feet\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"five weeks\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"around 16 hours\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"the project\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He hopes the micro-sculpture will travel to Paris to be exhibited during the Olympics to allow visitors to view his work.\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998528892, \"rank\": 1.472051870981369e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\"